translated: Janson, Stig, agronom, Moholm, b. 28/11/04 in Stockholm to shipowner Gustaf J. and Jenny Werner. Married on 31 with Karin MasOlle. Children: Barbro b. 31, Ulf 33, Annika 38. Agricultural expert in Ultuna from 28. Owned and operated Frändesta farm in Södermani from 28-47, owner of Ryholms estate in Västergötland since 47. Member of the Parliament's second chamber from 37-46, member of the appropriations committee, board member of the Bank of Ultuna from 44-47, chairman of the Helges tas:n municipal council from 31-42, municipal council member from 31-36 and pension council member from 31-35, chairman of the Södermani right-wing association from 38-47, chairman of the Sörmland agricultural central association board from 42-47, vice chairman of the Lantmännen slaughter industry association in Nyköping from 34-47, representative of the Swedish cereal association on the board from 35-36, member of the board of Swedish Cereal Inc. since 36 and the Swedish agricultural federation since 42, auditor of Södermani Enskilda Bank from 36-45, member of the provincial board of Skandinaviska Banken for Södermani from 45-47, chairman of the 46 committee for agricultural machinery evaluation, expert in several state investigations. Royal Order of the Vasa.
